data.description: Come home to the beach!  Sun and Sand lifestyle at the El Dorado.  The inviting and secured lobby with an elevator,  takes you up to this charming and spacious 1 bedroom, 1 Bath condo. Oversized windows in the dining area and living room allow plenty of sunlight to brighten your home. Enjoy all the closet space and storage in the large bedroom equipped with 2 closets and an alcove perfect for an office desk or reading area.  Use the private beach access to enjoy the enclosed community patio, and take in the nightly sunsets.  Conveniently located near Bluff Park, LB Museum of Art, Shoreline Village, and the downtown area.
